India won the toss and decided to bowl first in a crucial Nidahas Trophy T20 International against Sri Lanka at the Khettarama Stadium a short while ago.The match was delayed by 80 minutes due to rain and wet outfield.India has added KL Rahul and Rishabh Pant has to miss out.The game will be 19 overs a side and Sri Lanka has added Suranga Lakmal in place of suspended Dinesh Chandimal.